From a59bc2466ae0cdd6a7317f51aa0f4a3fe5caa796 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Logan Finney <loganfinney27@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 15:10:42 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] ci: pin all GitHub Actions references to full commit SHAs

Replaces tag-based action pins (@v4, @v6, etc.) with immutable commit
SHA pins across all 27 workflow files and the setup-vault composite
action. Enables the "Require actions to be pinned to full-length commit
SHA" org policy to be activated.

SHAs resolved 2026-04-17 from current tag heads.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
